                   \u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Cefalù\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository>Oratorio del Santissimo Sacramento, Piazza Duomo\u003C/repository>\n                     \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>A large block of grey limestone, built into the wall of a church. The lower right corner is missing, and the upper middle of the face shows cracking. Only the front face is visible in the current setting.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.limestone\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html\">limestone\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.block\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html\">block\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">88\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">103.5\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">unknown\u003C/depth>\n    